metadata.name: Alice in Metaland
metadata.description:
Alice in Metaland was inspired by my all time favorite literature, Alice in wonderland. 

My idea behind this project is to merge the borderline between a classic literature, pop culture memes and the Metaverse. 

Many Easter eggs are hidden in this piece including the CryptoPunks, Tungsten cube, Meta, Doge and much more to explore! 

Let's become a part of the Metaland.

Size : 2666 × 2000px
